data.description: Introducing a unique opportunity for investors or handy individuals seeking a project with great potential. This vacant two-family property, located in a desirable area, offers a "handyman special" that allows you to unleash your creativity and transform it into a remarkable investment.  The building boasts a compact yet functional size, measuring 17x30, providing ample space for customization and renovation. Situated on a generous 20x100 lot, there is room for expansion or outdoor enhancements to complement your vision.  With R5 zoning, this property offers flexibility in terms of usage and future development possibilities. Whether you envision a multi-unit rental property or a spacious single-family home, this property's zoning allows for various options to suit your needs.  It is important to note that this property requires a full gut renovation. While it may seem daunting, this presents an opportunity to create a space tailored to your preferences and specifications. With the right vision and investment, this property has the potential to become a stunning residence or a lucrative income-generating asset.
